&lt;h1 id="原理"&gt;原理&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;mcp (model context protocol) 模型文本协议&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;其中kali_server.py是放在kali端的 mcp_server.py是放在codex，claude或者其他agent端的 ，通过api调用kali上面的工具或者命令进行执行然后返回agnet端进行回应，通俗易懂的来说，指导kali的角色不再是人，而是agent，而人只需要指导agent的大致方向即可。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id="配置"&gt;配置&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;kali端&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-c" data-lang="c"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;python3&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;kali_server&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;py&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;--&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;port&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;5000&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;遇到这样的回显就成功了&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-c" data-lang="c"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;┌──&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;venv&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;─&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;kali&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;㉿&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;kali&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;~/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;Desktop&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;└─$&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;python3&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;kali_server&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;py&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;--&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;port&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;5000&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;2026&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mo"&gt;04&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;22&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mo"&gt;04&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;45&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;11&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;783&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="p"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;INFO&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;]&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;Starting&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;Kali&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;Linux&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;Tools&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;API&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;Server&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;on&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;port&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;5000&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;Serving&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;Flask&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;app&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="err"&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;kali_server&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;Debug&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nl"&gt;mode&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;off&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;2026&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mo"&gt;04&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;22&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mo"&gt;04&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;45&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;11&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;793&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="p"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;INFO&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;]&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nl"&gt;WARNING&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;This&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;is&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;a&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;development&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;server&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;Do&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;not&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;use&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;it&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;in&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;a&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;production&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;deployment&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;Use&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;a&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;production&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;WSGI&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;server&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;instead&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;Running&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;on&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;all&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nf"&gt;addresses&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mf"&gt;0.0.0.0&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;Running&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;on&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nl"&gt;http&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="c1"&gt;//127.0.0.1:5000
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;Running&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;on&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nl"&gt;http&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="c1"&gt;//61.139.2.130:5000
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;2026&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mo"&gt;04&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;22&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mo"&gt;04&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;45&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;11&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;794&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="p"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;INFO&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;]&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;Press&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;CTRL&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;+&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;C&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;to&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;quit&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;然后返回codex端&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;在设置-MCP服务器-添加服务器&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;然后那个mcp_server.py放在你想要放置的位置就好了&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;figure class="content-figure"&gt;
 &lt;img
 src="https://luxury-1393333723.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com//img/20260422173010133.png"
 alt="image.png"
 loading="lazy"
 decoding="async"
 &gt;
 
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id="测试"&gt;测试&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;重启codex 会发现mcp已经在运行了&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;figure class="content-figure"&gt;
 &lt;img
 src="https://luxury-1393333723.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com//img/20260422173112434.png"
 alt="image.png"
 loading="lazy"
 decoding="async"
 &gt;
 
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;在kali端 启动&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-c" data-lang="c"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;python3&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;kali_server&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;py&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;--&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;port&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;5000&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;回到codex&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;给codex命令&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;调用 kali 的 execute_command 工具，执行 pwd，并把返回结果告诉我&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;figure class="content-figure"&gt;
 &lt;img
 src="https://luxury-1393333723.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com//img/20260422173405222.png"
 alt="image.png"
 loading="lazy"
 decoding="async"
 &gt;
 
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;发现已经执行成功了&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-c" data-lang="c"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;2026&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mo"&gt;04&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;22&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mo"&gt;05&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mo"&gt;07&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;43&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;899&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="p"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;INFO&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;]&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mf"&gt;61.139.2.1&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="p"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;22&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;Apr&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;2026&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mo"&gt;05&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mo"&gt;07&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;43&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;]&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;#34;GET /health HTTP/1.1&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;200&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;2026&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mo"&gt;04&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;22&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mo"&gt;05&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;08&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;33&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mo"&gt;05&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;9&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="p"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;INFO&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;]&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;Executing&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nl"&gt;command&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;pwd&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;2026&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mo"&gt;04&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;22&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mo"&gt;05&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;08&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;33&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mo"&gt;063&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="p"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;INFO&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;]&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mf"&gt;61.139.2.1&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="p"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;22&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;Apr&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;2026&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mo"&gt;05&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;08&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;33&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;]&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;#34;POST /api/command HTTP/1.1&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;200&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;下面200 的 都是调用成功的&lt;/p&gt;
